        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 21–23. Plectanocnema nudipes. (21) male hypopygium, left face; (22) female, dorsal abdominal glands and the left dorsolateral gland (both stippled) that discharge between tergites 5 and 6 (T6 being vestigial in the middle third); (23) male, anterior face of hind tibia. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
